fields.value: John S. and James L. Knight Foundation Community Indicators

dsDescriptionValue.value: These data are part of an ongoing series sponsored by the Knight Foundation. The series evaluates community standing on dimensions such as citizenship, community development, education, children and social welfare, and arts and culture.

fields.value: Subject: Study Level Error Note, Notes: This survey used random digit dialing to sample adults 18 or older living in households with telephones in 26 different communities. The sample consists of a national sample and 26 community samples. Also included in 2002 are some regional and second city surveys for selected communities;
